N START -->\nBumping `nbconvert` to 7.17.1 without updating `mistune` from 0.8.4 to >=2.0.3 will cause runtime failures. `nbconvert` 7.x requires `mistune>=2.0.3,<4` because mistune 2.0 was a complete API rewrite (e.g., `BlockGrammar` was removed). The pinned `mistune==0.8.4` (marked `# via nbconvert`) is incompatible with this new version, and any code path that triggers nbconvert's markdown processing will crash with an `AttributeError`.\n<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->\n\n<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: ref1_886eb597-7476-45e3-a447-c2d9a68a69ef -->\n\n<!-- LOCATIONS START\npython/requirements_compiled.txt#L1199-L1200\npython/requirements_compiled_py3.13.txt#L1200-L1201\nLOCATIONS END -->\n<details>\n<summary>Additional Locations (1)</summary>\n\n- [`python/requirements_compiled_py3.13.txt#L1200-L1201`](https://github.com/ray-project/ray/blob/6d2bb0fc8e8544a028c9201bf5d844e1c59dc87a/python/requirements_compiled_py3.13.txt#L1200-L1201)\n\n</details>\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/open?data=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCIsImtpZCI6ImJ1Z2JvdC12MiJ9..rlJwUsCIZEmHl-Z0BeDlN5FLNQg-W-aPaLjDT5zBOHTNVp7KXYCuvXQFly1VusgMaFsy0KSVXtQuSE-dfgjI0Xj_6_aQKtRMBkyx6f-pVeRi7y8L-r2wn5HAKVz6pYEdI88mFQiaJts7X92g4cNQjMRsl9RTGQZeJjXG1C7FDD41whiuTSsIB-yJmMd4NHVaTI_JlpmmziqRroDZoZKNp7pvsI06wghscdW5fw6HDAKJ3UZHkNbDnq6akjhAZxqKOs3Llw0GNWCy2P9yheyfnCM2BxzCrST3yVh_-IYztw6xjsr6uK9P3tJWswnHuxOeY77jTTONO5DhJRASVI4LCA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Cursor\" width=\"115\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?data=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCIsImtpZCI6ImJ1Z2JvdC12MiJ9..dsdlVnkPvF2cocdtwhjLlmi5_P8uDFyCJdCmtTemuA81g-BMPGuqtlhRhKVl9rCJqG-bk70u0